    public class NavigationFeedbackService
extends java.lang.Object
implements RouteNavigator.RouteNavigatorListener, RouteNavigationManager.RouteNavigationManagerEventListener
    Responsible for providing feedback (speed, distance, eta, voice cues, vibration, etc.) throughout navigation.
